data.description: Classic, Real Brick Deltona home-Ready for it's new owners. Spacious split plan with a popular layout is perfect for get togethers and entertaining.  The living room, dining room combo has plenty of natural light with French Doors leading to the huge Florida Room and the private yard beyond.  The kitchen has ample storage and work area and opens to the dinette area and family room with an exceptional brick wall fireplace.  A very impressive Florida Room measures 30' x 12', has easy functional screen/vinyl windows and it's own separate A/C system.  ROOF 2019. UPDATED PANEL BOX 2019.  Just minutes is the Fabulous, FUN Dewey Booster Sports Complex with Baseball, Soccer & Football fields, hiking trail, multiple picnic and playground areas and even a stage for outdoor performances.  Convenient Convenient location to I-4, shopping, restaurants and hospitals.
